        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Industrial Control Systems Cybersecurity Training Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes within the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency an initiative to provide the cybersecurity workforce with no-cost training related to securing industrial control systems. These are information systems used to control industrial processes, such as manufacturing, product handling, production, and distribution.</p>]]>
        </text>
